data.description: Experience peaceful living with this stunning custom-built Lindal cedar home, situated on a serene 1 acre knoll with spectacular panoramic views of mountains/valley/streams, trees & garden flora. Boasting an open concept design with spacious lanais, this breathtaking home is located on a private drive near the tranquil Lawai stream with a secluded waterfall just minutes away.    Meticulously maintained with pride of ownership with an array of impressive upgrades including solar electric, solar hot-water, gas stove, custom remote control blinds, custom shelving throughout, granite countertops, DeWils Maple cabinetry, bamboo flooring on the 1st level, remodeled bathrooms, covered decking off the kitchen & attached in-law quarters, new roof (Certainteed solar reflective shingles) in 2022 with transferable warranty, outdoor shower, workshop area & storage area for beach gear/surfboards/kayaks, open beam knotty pine T&G vaulted ceilings and Western Red Cedar siding. The primary bathroom has a custom travertine double shower, granite counters, glass vessel sinks, African ribbon mahogany vanities and a new jacuzzi tub. With 27 solar panels with a transferable maintenance contract, you'll enjoy energy-efficient living.  Spread over 2,865 sq ft of living space, the 4 bedroom / 3.5 bath floor plan provides ample room to entertain while providing guests with privacy via a separate entrance. High ceilings & windows galore warmly illuminate the tropical views of the surrounding valley.  You'll love the private area that could be used for a gym, game room, family room or artist area with access to the yard. On the lawn, the eye is drawn to the visual accent of a pavilion gazebo and an abundance of tropical flowers & fruit trees.  This property's favorable Agriculture zoning widens the horizons for footprint expansion. The home is conveniently located to many south shore beaches, 6 miles from Poipu and 11 miles to Lihue with shopping/dining options, hospital and airport.
